    <h1 {...{
      "id": "fonts-cli"
    }}>{`Fonts CLI`}</h1>
    <p>{`This tool is a wrapper to help download/rename fonts to fit with the font naming conventions.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "conventions"
    }}>{`Conventions`}</h2>
    <p>{`For naming files, ensure that names are in lowercase format and that the numerals are replaced with common weight names (the renaming can be done with code).`}</p>
    <p>{`We keep things lower case for purposes of serving on web, and replacing the numerals with the common font name is just an addition.`}</p>
    <p>{`To see the conventional name for font weights, `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://medium.com/react-native-training/react-native-custom-fonts-ccc9aacf9e5e"
      }}>{`Mozilla has a reference here.`}</a></p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "examples"
    }}>{`Examples`}</h3>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="thead">
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`Example name`}</th>
          <th parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`After renaming`}</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody parentName="table">
        <tr parentName="tbody">
          <td parentName="tr" {...{
            "align": null
          }}>{`SourceSansPro-200.ttf`}</td>
